<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7661580>
    dc:description "Figs 15, 16. Uroplectes adults, habitus in life: (15) U. gracilior Hewitt, 1913, male; (16) U. planimanus (Karsch, 1879), female with brood." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7661580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7661552>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Brandberg Massif (Namibia), gravel plains southwest, facing northeast to Massif in distance, dry year. Gravel plains, habitat of Parabuthus brevimanus (Thorell, 1876), Parabuthus namibensis Lamoral, 1979 and Uroplectes gracilior Hewitt, 1913." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7661552/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

